---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

const {title, tags, src, stars} = Astro.props
---


<div
  class="border bg-card text-card-foreground max-w-md mx-auto shadow-lg rounded-lg overflow-hidden hover:scale-105 transition"
  data-v0-t="card"
>
  <Image
    src={src}
    alt="Project Image"
    class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
    width="400"
    height="200"
    style="aspect-ratio: 400 / 200; object-fit: cover;"
  />
  <div class="p-4">
    <h3 class="whitespace-nowrap tracking-tight text-xl font-bold">{title}</h3>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-2">
      <span class="inline-block bg-gray-200 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mr-2 mb-2">
        #javascript
      </span>
      <span class="inline-block bg-gray-200 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mr-2 mb-2">
        #react
      </span>
      <span class="inline-block bg-gray-200 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mr-2 mb-2">
        #tailwindcss
      </span>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 my-2">
      This is a brief description of the web development project. It covers the main technologies used, the purpose
      of the project, and the main challenges faced during development.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-4 bg-gray-900 p-4 rounded-lg">
    <div class="flex gap-2 content-stretch">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Customer Review </h3>
      {Array(5).fill(0).map((_, i) => <svg
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        fill="currentColor"
        class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-200"
        viewBox="0 0 20 20"
        >
        <path d="M10 15.27L16.18 19l-1.64-7.03L20 7.24l-7.19-.61L10 0 7.19 6.63 0 7.24l5.46 4.73L3.82 19z"></path>
        </svg>)}

    </div>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        "This team did an excellent job on our project. They were responsive, professional, and delivered
        high-quality work. We're thrilled with the results and would highly recommend them to others."
      </p>
      <div class="flex items-center mt-2">
        
      </div>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">- Jane Doe, CEO of XYZ Corp</p>
    </div>
    <a
      class="mt-4 inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-gray-900 px-8 text-sm font-medium text-gray-50 shadow transition-colors hover:bg-gray-900/90 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-gray-950 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 dark:bg-gray-50 dark:text-gray-900 dark:hover:bg-gray-50/90 dark:focus-visible:ring-gray-300"
      href="#"
    >
      View Project
    </a>
  </div>
</div>